name: Darkblood Eviscerator
description: The Darkblood have dwelled behind the walls surrounding the city of Falguard for centuries, but there are those who venture beyond these walls. Those that do journey to the outside world are just looking for one thing and two things only… Punishment and Suffering! To operate these arm blades click the top of the hilt to extend the blade and click the bottom of the blade to access its magical glyphs.
